&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This means that host_ is null.&lt;br/&gt;
Maybe you&apos;re passing null sometimes ?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But the code is admittedly strange in that it checks the length field without null check.&lt;br/&gt;
